description: Demolition of existing structures and redevelopment of the site to provide 518 residential units including affordable housing (Use Class C3) and 3,150 sq m of flexible commercial floorspace comprising a mix of retail floorspace (Class A1 - A3); business (Class B1); leisure (Class D2) in new buildings ranging between 5 to 13 storeys in height, together with associated car parking and cycle storage, landscaping and associated infrastructure works including private and communal space together with public realm improvements.
